<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>I would like to suggest that some improvements be made to Zend_View, mainly to promote the use of fluent interfaces. I see that some components are doing this but it has not been widely implemented. I believe most of the add and set methods in this object lend themselves well to a fluent interface.</p>

<p>Could this possibly be suggested across the board for all the components?</p>

<p>P.S. This is my first time ever contributing so if I've done this in the wrong place, I apologise.</p>

